<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">March</TIMEX> Comments at <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">187</NUMEX> (comment of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Michael</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">L. Monahan</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">State Bar of Georgia</ENAMEX>). Private <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">attorneys</ENAMEX> who engage
