Private <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">counsel</ENAMEX> also lack expertise in legal claims under the
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">H</ENAMEX><ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">-2A</ENAMEX> program. See <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">March</TIMEX> Comments at <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">21</NUMEX> (comment of <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Robert J.</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Willis</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">Attorney</ENAMEX> at <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Law</ENAMEX>); <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">March</TIMEX> Comments at <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">130</NUMEX> (comment of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Shelley</ENAMEX>
