<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">North Carolina</ENAMEX>); <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">April</TIMEX> Comments at <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">104</NUMEX> (comment of <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Garry G.</ENAMEX>
Geffert, <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">West Virginia</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Legal Services</ENAMEX> Plan). Representing H-2A
<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">workers</ENAMEX> typically requires specialized knowledge of the H-2A
