Finally, as with the representation of other alien <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">farmworkers</ENAMEX>,
private <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">attorneys</ENAMEX> typically do not have the language skills,
special resources and knowledge necessary to maintain contact with
a <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">client</ENAMEX>, who resides <NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">thousands of miles</NUMEX> from their <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">office</ENAMEX> and does
not have a telephone or regular mail delivery, and who may not even
know the name of his <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">employer</ENAMEX>. See <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">March</TIMEX> Comments at <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">20</NUMEX> (comment of
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Robert J. Willis</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">Attorney</ENAMEX> at <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Law</ENAMEX>); see also <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">March</TIMEX> Comments at <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">235</NUMEX>
