<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE_DESC">States</ENAMEX>. The category of permanent <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">residents</ENAMEX> includes commuter
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">aliens</ENAMEX>, who work in the <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">United States</ENAMEX> but whose actual <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC">residence</ENAMEX> is
