As applied to the situation of unrestricted <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">aliens</ENAMEX>, the three
interpretations of the presence requirement suggested in the
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Federal Register</ENAMEX> notice would lead to unintended and absurd
